tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE performance_analytics (
    analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    quiz_score INT,
    assignment_score INT,
    exam_score INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students(student_id)
);
CREATE TABLE student_progress ( student_id INT, course_id INT, progress INT );
CREATE TABLE grades ( student_id INT, course_id INT, grade VARCHAR(2) );
CREATE TABLE performance_analytics ( student_id INT, course_id INT, total_attempts INT, correct_attempts INT, incorrect_attempts INT );
CREATE TABLE courses ( course_id INT, course_name VARCHAR(50) );
